For each user story or feature:

| Test Case / Feature         | Automation Feasible (Y/N) | Priority | Notes                           |
| --------------------------- | ------------------------- | -------- | ------------------------------- |
| Login functionality         | Yes âœ…                     | High     | Stable, used in all test cycles |
| UI theme changes            | No âŒ                      | Low      | Too visual                      |
